# Project Setup

This is a React application built with Vite and TypeScript.

- The main entry point is likely [coderx/src/main.tsx](mdc:coderx/src/main.tsx).
- The root application component is likely [coderx/src/App.tsx](mdc:coderx/src/App.tsx).
- Vite configuration is managed in [coderx/vite.config.ts](mdc:coderx/vite.config.ts). This includes aliasing `@` to the `src` directory and deduplicating `react` and `react-dom` to prevent hook errors.
- Dependencies are managed in [package.json](mdc:package.json).
